Zoleka Mandela just keeps shedding those unwanted kilos. And she looks incredible! Zoleka embarked on a fitness mission last year and so far she's dropped over 19kgs. The author shared a collage of smoking-hot pictures of herself in a little black dress. "This housewife has lost over 19kgs, reached her goal weight of 70kgs by her 37th birthday and has lost an additional 3kgs ... I'm currently in the 66kgs region from weighing 86.4kgs," she said. That's impressive.